  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK393">
<l>kaṇṇuṭaiya reṉpavar kaṟṟōr mukattiraṇṭu</l>
<l>puṇṇuṭaiyar kallā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learned are said to have eyes, but the unlearned have (merely) two sores in their face.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
